- Use fractal noise for organic feel
- Ensure tileable pattern

## Configuration Structure Requirements

### Plugin Requirements
```javascript
plugins: [require("tailwindcss-animate")]
```

**Rules:**
- Always include `tailwindcss-animate` for smooth transitions
- Maintain existing plugin compatibility

### Content Configuration
```javascript
content: [
  "./src/pages/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx,mdx}",
  "./src/components/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx,mdx}", 
  "./src/app/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx,mdx}",
]
```

**Rules:**
- Include all source directories
- Support both JS and TS file extensions
- Include MDX support for documentation

### Dark Mode Support
```javascript
darkMode: ["class"]
```

**Rules:**
- Use class-based dark mode strategy
- Maintain compatibility with theme switching

## Anti-Patterns to Avoid

### ❌ Generic Color Names
```javascript
// Don't use generic color names
colors: {
  'primary': '#D98666', // Too generic
  'secondary': '#88A89A', // Too generic
}

// Use semantic, material-based names
colors: {
  'terracotta': '#D98666', // ✅ Evokes natural material
  'sage': '#88A89A', // ✅ Evokes natural color
}
```

### ❌ Perfect Geometric Shapes
```javascript
// Don't use perfect geometric border radius
borderRadius: {
  'button': '8px', // Too geometric
  'card': '12px', // Too geometric
}

// Use organic, asymmetric shapes
borderRadius: {
  'squircle': '2rem 1rem 1rem 2rem', // ✅ Organic asymmetry
}
```

### ❌ Standard Material Shadows
```javascript
// Don't use standard shadow values
boxShadow: {
  'md': '0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1)', // Too standard
}

// Use custom paper-like shadows
boxShadow: {
  'paper': '0 4px 6px -1px rgba(43, 42, 45, 0.1), ...', // ✅ Multi-layered
}
```